[b]Spitting Cobra[/b]
3’ long snakes with grey/white scales, prefer to attack from a distance with spit.

AC 7 [[b][/b]12], HD 1* (4hp), Att 1 × spit (blindness) or 1 × bite (1d3 + poison), THAC0 19 [0], MV 90’ (30’), SV D12 W13 P14 B15 S16 (1), ML 7, AL Neutral, XP 13, NA 1d6 (1d6), TT None

[b]Blinding spit:[/b] Range: 6’. A hit causes permanent blindness (save vs poison).
[b]Poison:[/b] Causes death in 1d10 turns (save versus poison).
